{"sn27.1:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 27.1 ","sn27.1:0.2":"1. Kilesavagga ","sn27.1:0.3":"Cakkhusutta ","sn27.1:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn27.1:1.2":"“Yo, bhikkhave, cakkhusmim chandarago, cittasseso upakkileso. ","sn27.1:1.3":"Yo sotasmim chandarago, cittasseso upakkileso. ","sn27.1:1.4":"Yo ghanasmim chandarago, cittasseso upakkileso. ","sn27.1:1.5":"Yo jivhaya chandarago, cittasseso upakkileso. ","sn27.1:1.6":"Yo kayasmim chandarago, cittasseso upakkileso. ","sn27.1:1.7":"Yo manasmim chandarago, cittasseso upakkileso. ","sn27.1:1.8":"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno imesu chasu thanesu cetaso upakkileso pahino hoti, nekkhammaninnancassa cittam hoti. ","sn27.1:1.9":"Nekkhammaparibhavitam cittam kammaniyam khayati, abhinna sacchikaraniyesu dhammesu”ti. ","sn27.1:1.10":"Pathamam. "}